Title: Field Medic Investigate Hospital
Descriptions: Reports are coming in — a hospital in Stary Sobor was ambushed by bandits. Medical supplies were taken, and survivors are missing. This won't be easy... You'll need a vehicle to reach the area and deal with the threat. Gear up and be ready for a fight.
Goto the location find out if there were any survivors
The hospital is secured, and the bandits are no more. You did what others couldn’t. Thank you — this reward is well-deserved.
ObjectiveText: Travel to Hospital and locate Bandits
